Package: theta
Type: Package
Title: Co-occurrence based measure of species habitat specialization
Version: 0.8-02
Date: 2026-01-02
Author: David Zeleny, partly based on published scripts by Fridley et al. (2007), Zeleny (2009), Botta-Dukat (2012) and Zeleny & Chytry (2019)
Maintainer: David Zeleny <zeleny.david@gmail.com>
Description: Calculates theta, the co-occurrence based measure of species habitat
    specialization, introduced by Fridley et al. 2007. The package contains function
    optimized for use on large datasets, and offers several beta diversity metrics as a statistcs.
Imports:
    vegan,
    RColorBrewer,
    vegetarian,
    parallel,
    betapart,
    ade4,
    cati,
    stats,
    graphics,
    utils,
    simcom
Encoding: UTF-8
